  {
    "uuid": "482a00b8-5392-5b91-ba51-ddb945c941e2",
    "entry": "順向",
    "reading": {
      "primary": "じゅんこう",
      "alternatives": [],
      "is_heteronym": false
    },
    "grammar": {
      "pos": [
        "名詞-の形容詞",
        "形容詞-語幹"
      ],
      "ctype": null,
      "inflections": null
    },
    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "proactive",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "彼は常に順向的な思考を持っており、過去の失敗を悔やむより未来の対策を優先する。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "組織の改革には、現状を維持しようとする後ろ向きな姿勢ではなく、順向的な意欲が必要だ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "試験前に新しい知識を詰め込みすぎたせいで、順向干渉が起きて以前覚えた内容が混同してしまった。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      }
    ],
    "relations": {
      "homophones": [],
      "synonyms": [],
      "antonyms": [],
      "related": []
    },
